Package com.ftp.file

Class FTPTransferObject

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ftp.file.FTPTransferObject
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class FTPTransferObject
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    This is main class used for communicating between server and client. It contains file parameters, client username and password needed for authorizing requests, FTPCommand for executing request on server side, response code and message that are returned from server after executing command, and additional data as byte array that is primarily used for sending file explorer as TreeItem to client.
